{"tid":1435144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔諗下做廢物回收重用餵popo","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:29:12.000Z","uid":37679,"like":129,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7fc7d35f99a1946aa693127f061f54495d81d3","tid":1435144,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"街市啲豬牛肉檔<br />\n日日切埋切埋咁多內臟脂肪唔要<br />\n又臭又腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔去餵popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一嚟唔使錢 <br />\n我地幫佢地收垃圾佢地多謝我地都嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二嚟可以直接整臭佢哋啲gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又臭又油 hi埋hi埋 成套都未必用得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三嚟 感觀上差 但點都冇火喺中立眼中咁激進<br />\n又唔使增加消防負擔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔會有咩危險性 最多係驚掟到記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5e514308a08281759c438d10371b5f229d2650","tid":1435144,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:46.