脂肪唔要<br />\n又臭又腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔去餵popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一嚟唔使錢 <br />\n我地幫佢地收垃圾佢地多謝我地都嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二嚟可以直接整臭佢哋啲gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又臭又油 hi埋hi埋 成套都未必用得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三嚟 感觀上差 但點都冇火喺中立眼中咁激進<br />\n又唔使增加消防負擔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔會有咩危險性 最多係驚掟到記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"圍狗個陣仲可以砌佢老母生豬肉<br />\n一野抆落去佢個頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa3b5e359f1ea2588499c7dc533b6fc38854d25","tid":1435144,"uid":173800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28456ebb44fa6dfcbab0f2b7056c94c677c5f082","tid":1435144,"uid":37679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"155e756e6d7ae7953e29152cc0e501ac565900f5","tid":1435144,"uid":173800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor